      "title": "Change in price",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Litro company has informed that the price of Litro cooking gas will be reduced by 100-200 rupees from midnight tomorrow (5).",
        "Mr. Muditha Peiris, President of Litro Company, said that in the last two months, Litro Company has made a lot of profit and in August alone, Litro Company has made a profit of more than 700 million.",
        "However, even if the price of cooking gas is reduced, the price of food items cannot be reduced, said Asela Sampath, President of the Canteen Owners Association."
      ],
